data.name: lblUpdateAgain.Text
data.value: * In-case someone has committed changes after you clicked "Update", you have to update again. Otherwise, the commit will fail.

data.name: lblHeader.Text
data.value: You have chosen to recommend revision {0} of '{1}'. After a revision is recommended, every SVN-Monitor user that has defined this source will be notified of this recommendation and will be suggested to update to this revision.

data.name: lblRecommend.Text
data.value: Click the "Recommend" button to recommend the revision. It will modify the root folder of the source, so you'll need to commit.

data.name: lblUpdate.Text
data.value: In-order to recommend a revision, the source needs to be updated to the latest revision (HEAD). Click the "Update" button to update your source and resolve any conflicts you might have.

data.name: lblCommit.Text
data.value: After recommending the revision, the local source is modified. In-order to notify other SVN-Monitor users, the source needs to be committed. Click the "Commit" button to commit the changes and close this wizard.
